name: WhatColorsintheRainbow
0:
”Alexa, ask maddie's leprechaun what colors are in the rainbow.”
”Alexa, ask maddie's leprechaun how many colors are in the rainbow.”
”Alexa, ask maddie's leprechaun what colors are there in the rainbow.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: maddie's leprechaun
des: Ask leprechaun how many colors and what colors are in the rainbow! Perfect for young kids who are learning. Pair this skill with color cards to teach your kids what color is which. Don't want your toddler thinking violet is orange!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
